Package org.bukkit.inventory.meta

Interface SuspiciousStewMeta

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, ConfigurationSerializable, ItemMeta, PersistentDataHolder
public interface SuspiciousStewMeta
extends ItemMeta
Represents a suspicious stew that can have custom effects.
